entries.femaleVariant: So, ya got the book?
Bought the book.
Got something interesting here...
Ya got my eddies?
All yours.
That's not nice.
Ehh. So be it. All yours.
Who do you think I am, Nix? Some slumpup you can fuck as you please without any consequences?
Not sellin' at that price. Need more.
Not willin' to pay me near enough. I'm 'onna keep it.
Hold on, hold on… I'll pay you double. That suit you?
The net's my home. I know its history. And I know the spellbook's worth several times more than you're offerin'.
Uh, sorry, V. No hard feelings. Had no idea.
As I says, V. I am a serious man.
Amount as agreed, all yours.
Thanks.
Tablet's worth heaps more. You know it, I know it.
Thanks a bunch.
Don't mention it. It's money well-deserved.
The tablet's worth heaps more. I know that and you know that.
Uh… hold on, hold on, hold on.
Maybe it is. But I offered you a price and you accepted it.
Any contract can be declared null and void when a party thereto's proven to have acted in bad faith.
A'ight. Have it your way. You are hereby awarded a bonus.
Pleasure doin' business with ya. Later.
V... word of advice. Don't pull shit like that with me. Just don't.
Came into this thing... a Zetatech XPR. Last owner claimed it houses old soft, datin' back before the first Net's crash.
Give it here, lemme have a look…
Naw, data's corrupt… Worthless heap o' junk as I see it.
Buuut... I'll buy this off ya. Got a soft spot for old tech, feel me?
Thanks, V. You on the level, girl.
entries.maleVariant: Thanks, V. You on the level, my man.

entries.femaleVariant: Fine, you'll get a fair price. With some ennies on top by way of an apology. How's that sound?
Sounds right.
Fuck you.
Sounds right.
Got a head on them shoulders, V. Respect.
Fuck you, Nix.
Hold on, V. Nobody's gonna pay you more for that tablet.
Like I give a shit. Just gonna make sure it never lands in your hands.
Suits me just fine.
Pay me triple and it's yours...
Gonna keep it.
Pay me triple... and it's yours.
Motherfucker, these kids today... But OK, deal.
Nix, don't try that again. Just fuckin' don't.
Know what? Think I'll keep it.
Ain't nobody gonna match what I'm willin' to give you for that heap o' junk.
Make up your mind, Nix. What is it? Worth twice what you offered at first, or is it junk?
Lies got no legs, Nix. And liars got legs with broken knees. Suggest you remember that.
Saved your fuckin' life.
